Package es.utils.mapper.getter Description

Provides the implementation of the abstract Getter operation and its implementations.
The package contains the following getter types:
  • Getter : handle the logic of a generic getter operation
  • FunctionGetter (sub-class of Getter) : create a Getter instance from a Function
  • FieldGetter (sub-class of FunctionGetter) : create a Getter instance from a Field
  • SupplierGetter (sub-class of FunctionGetter) : create a Getter instance from a Supplier
  • ValueGetter (sub-class of SupplierGetter) : create a Getter instance from a constant value
Author:
eschoysman
See Also:
Getter, FunctionGetter, FieldGetter, SupplierGetter, ValueGetter
